data.title: Top A Site Dash Refract Execute
data.description: Use this unpredictable, yet effective Light Speed lineup to catch any Defenders on site off-guard. This is a great way to execute after your Initiators have provided you information on the enemy's positioning.

data.title: Top C Site Dash + Long Refract
data.description: Quickly entry onto the site with this Light Speed lineup to make yourself unpredictable to Defenders playing Default. This also allows you to seek an early off-angle engagement to rewind back to C Long safely.
